{"tid":1273761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讀多次宣言呀！班記者聽唔到呀！","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:51:39.000Z","uid":9348,"like":363,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"001239cf5b85b6292ff2a5aec735ad01f7f9d19a","tid":1273761,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdc39c9dc3e8e37d671703e1a7d73c0b0a31fd5","tid":1273761,"uid":13984,"like":329,"dislike":2,"score":327,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2300開記招全部記者2300去主席台</span></span>"},{"pid":"06afc11e7ca18a2514b60d598ad7a6834058f42a","tid":1273761,"uid":269578,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cbc9534321f995cbb2f8a08c280255f4cc55f2","tid":1273761,"uid":79181,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"文宣幫傳<br />\n提防散水 <br />\n人少先危險<br />\n唔好信擇日再戰<br />\n全力支援現場決定<br />\n議員請保護留守義士<br />\n發夢香港人盡快出去支援準備反包圍<br />\n發夢需要各種補給<br />\n發夢需要照明燈<br />\n一定要頂住 堅持住！<br />\n香港要改變！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不撤不散<br />\n<br />\n一定要捉住今次機會<br />\n絕對唔好再浪費<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"b567e5b96a7b3143044a8cfcd2ec1978788e3c53","tid":1273761,"uid":267337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5a46e5afb4321df09ead675316cdbdcee384873","tid":1273761,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"745dbc43859039e130e728f00230a0a8cffc65ec","tid":1273761,"uid":236925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:52:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4acb56747736102ef696b5b7e261d4c28cb78a5","tid":1273761,"uid":1037,"like